name: mylunch Ltd
tag_list: lunch, lunch-offers, lunch-deals, lunch-specials, lunch-vouchers, lunch-in-dublin
overview:
mylunch.ie is a Dublin-based website that provides consumers with an online platform of lunch information.

Updated on a daily basis, the site lists the latest lunch specials, lunch menus & lunch offers of restaurants, cafes and bars in Dublin and across Ireland.

The company is in direct contact with lunch retailers on a daily basis and works with them to help them better target their target audience in the online realm.

For more information about the company and to get involved see http://www.mylunch.ie
